member.summary: Adds a Namespace to a collector of namespaces. Note that at the time this method is called, the Namespace added may not be complete. It's Name property and Parent properties may not have been set. For this reason, implementors of this interface should keep the added Namespaces in a temporary list, and process them later (e.g., move them from the temporary list to a Hashtable keyed off of the FullName property) when ResolveAddedNamespaces() is called.

member.name: M:DevExpress.CodeRush.StructuralParser.INamespaceCollector.ResolveAddedNamespaces
